<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>心理学 on 📖 爱分享读书</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/tags/%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/</link><description>Recent content in 心理学 on 📖 爱分享读书</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://www.ishareread.com/tags/%E5%BF%83%E7%90%86%E5%AD%A6/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>当生活把你逼到墙角，如何体面地撑过去？</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E5%BD%93%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%8A%8A%E4%BD%A0%E9%80%BC%E5%88%B0%E5%A2%99%E8%A7%92%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%93%E9%9D%A2%E5%9C%B0%E6%92%91%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB/</link><pubDate>Thu, 14 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E5%BD%93%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB%E6%8A%8A%E4%BD%A0%E9%80%BC%E5%88%B0%E5%A2%99%E8%A7%92%E5%A6%82%E4%BD%95%E4%BD%93%E9%9D%A2%E5%9C%B0%E6%92%91%E8%BF%87%E5%8E%BB/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;你有没有过这样的时刻？明明已经拼尽全力，却还是被生活逼得喘不过气。早上一睁眼就是待还的房贷，工作上遇到瓶颈想突破却无从下手，家里老人身体不好需要照顾，孩子的教育问题又让人头疼，好不容易想找个朋友倾诉，翻开通讯录却发现不知道该打给谁。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>为什么你总被职场PUA拿捏？读懂阿德勒这本人性说明书，终于清醒了</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BD%A0%E6%80%BB%E8%A2%AB%E8%81%8C%E5%9C%BApua%E6%8B%BF%E6%8D%8F%E8%AF%BB%E6%87%82%E9%98%BF%E5%BE%B7%E5%8B%92%E8%BF%99%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%E4%BA%86/</link><pubDate>Sat, 09 May 2026 00:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/%E4%B8%BA%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E4%BD%A0%E6%80%BB%E8%A2%AB%E8%81%8C%E5%9C%BApua%E6%8B%BF%E6%8D%8F%E8%AF%BB%E6%87%82%E9%98%BF%E5%BE%B7%E5%8B%92%E8%BF%99%E6%9C%AC%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%A7%E8%AF%B4%E6%98%8E%E4%B9%A6%E7%BB%88%E4%BA%8E%E6%B8%85%E9%86%92%E4%BA%86/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 为什么你总被职场PUA拿捏？读懂阿德勒这本人性说明书，终于清醒了" /&gt;&lt;hr&gt;
&lt;p&gt;你有没有过这种感觉——&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;明明干了很多活，领导一句&amp;quot;你这水平，离开公司谁要你？&amp;ldquo;就能让你整宿睡不着。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;明明不是你的错，同事一句阴阳怪气，你却反复琢磨自己哪里得罪了人。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>58岁还在乘风破浪，我们有什么资格谈晚了？</title><link>https://www.ishareread.com/p/58%E5%B2%81%E8%BF%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B9%98%E9%A3%8E%E7%A0%B4%E6%B5%AA%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%B5%84%E6%A0%BC%E8%B0%88%E6%99%9A%E4%BA%86/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2026 20:00:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://www.ishareread.com/p/58%E5%B2%81%E8%BF%98%E5%9C%A8%E4%B9%98%E9%A3%8E%E7%A0%B4%E6%B5%AA%E6%88%91%E4%BB%AC%E6%9C%89%E4%BB%80%E4%B9%88%E8%B5%84%E6%A0%BC%E8%B0%88%E6%99%9A%E4%BA%86/</guid><description>&lt;img src="https://www.ishareread.com/" alt="Featured image of post 58岁还在乘风破浪，我们有什么资格谈晚了？" /&gt;&lt;p&gt;你有过那种瞬间吗？&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;刷手机时，看到一条热搜：58岁的萧蔷在《乘风2026》的舞台上，一个180度一字马惊艳全场。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;评论区炸了。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;有人惊叹：&amp;ldquo;这状态，说是28岁我都信。&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>